<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Student Support Services</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Acıbadem University offers internship and job opportunities through its Career Center, which hosts a “Career Fair” with over 100 companies each year. Academic advisors assist with course planning and career guidance. The Psychological Support Unit offers free therapy for exam stress and adjustment issues. The Office for Students with Disabilities ensures campus accessibility and exam accommodations. The Scholarship Office provides full scholarships for 205 medical students and 25–100% discounts for other departments. The mentoring program connects first-year students with upperclassmen for academic and social support.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-10-27T08:54:00Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2025-10-27T08:54:01Z') WHERE "collection" = 'pages' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_pages" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'acibadem-university' );
